INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('286', '1', '2011-01-05 18:32:18', '2011-01-05 18:32:18', '<h3>our sale packages</h3>\r\nWe at Queens Park Real Estates have devised 3 different packages tailored to suit the marketing and sale requirements of your property and are as follows;\r\n<div class=\"cols3container\">\r\n<div class=\"col blue\">\r\n<div class=\"contentContainer\">\r\n<h2>Band A</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\r\n	<li>12 months online and offline advertisement  via the internet and all other marketing portals</li>\r\n	<li>Currently we advertise on our website and other popular and most visited property marketing sites around the world.</li>\r\n	<li>You are in total control of the advertisement of your property; all you need do is open an account with us, supply details of your property, upload pictures, and any other details you know would best portray the property.</li>\r\n	<li>You decide how you want applicants to contact you and they contact you directly</li>\r\n	<li>You arrange viewings at your convenience and negotiate the best price for your property</li>\r\n	<li>You can have the property on our site for 12months giving you enough time to advertise and complete.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>1 Property = £100 per year</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>2 Properties = £150 per year</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>more than 2 properties = £150 + £25 per extra property per year\r\n</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class=\"signUP\" href=\"http://www.queensparkrealestates.co.uk/my-account/\">Order this package</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col orange\">\r\n<h2>Band B</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\r\n	<li>All options from <strong>Band A</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Property Valuation is provided</li>\r\n	<li>Professional pictures, floor plans and other document required by law are provided</li>\r\n	<li>Advice you as to simple improvements that can be made to the property to increase Value</li>\r\n	<li>Properties are marketed by our local representative in your region (please co